1. System Administrator Access
The system administrator login has full read and write access, including permissions to edit any customer account, delete records, and manage global data.
Username: admin
Password: admin

2. Staff Coordinator Accounts (Personalized Data Access)
Staff coordinators can only view their own assigned records, submit new tasks/reports, and cannot modify previous records or other staff members' data.
Password: staff123 (or the worker's own name in lowercase, e.g., celine)
